reviewText: Pleased with purchase- good workout and I enjoy Charlene Prickets information on health  and staying fit. Need to keep the heart in good shape as well as the body.

The Charlene Prickett workout not on;y provides an enjoyable and rigorous workout, but very useful information is also provided so that a viewer can better understand the importance of the health benefits of the workout and also the specific effects upon the body.  The tape in three words can be described as fun, informative, and rigorous. I have used the tape for years and never tire of it.
